                            <comment id="12921346" author="rcmuir" created="Fri, 15 Oct 2010 13:21:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch that uses Assume.assumeNoException&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if the test cannot connect to the URL (), instead of seeing 5 tests pass, you will only see 4.&lt;br/&gt;
(The test is treated as if it were @Ignore, so the output looks like the below)&lt;/p&gt;

